===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{liushu|j}}, but of what is unclear: 
* Variant of {{och-l|玄}} with an elongated stroke to distinguish (Ji Xusheng).
* Abbreviation of {{och-l|縣}} (He Linyi).

{{Shuowen}} mistakes it for an inversion of {{och-l|予}} based on its seal script form. This misinterpretation has produced the variant form {{och-l|*𠄔}} through ''{{w|liding}}'' ({{zh-l|*隸定}}). This variant is sometimes mistakenly presented as evidence of the character's origin in popular media.

